sequenceDiagram
    participant S2 as System-2 (Target)
    participant KEA as Kea DHCP (System-1)
    participant TFTP as TFTP (System-1)
    participant HTTP as HTTP (System-1:80)
    participant REG as Registry (System-1:5000)

    Note over S2: Power On (PXE)
    S2->>KEA: DHCP Discover
    KEA->>S2: Offer 10.0.0.102 + boot-file: undionly.kpxe
    S2->>TFTP: GET undionly.kpxe
    TFTP->>S2: iPXE binary

    Note over S2: iPXE loaded
    S2->>KEA: DHCP Discover (iPXE user-class)
    KEA->>S2: Offer 10.0.0.102 + boot-file: autoexec.ipxe
    S2->>TFTP: GET autoexec.ipxe
    TFTP->>S2: Boot script (MAC routing)

    Note over S2: Kernel + Initramfs + Rootfs
    S2->>HTTP: GET kernel, initramfs, rootfs (~1GB)
    HTTP->>S2: FCOS live assets (local, fast)

    Note over S2: FCOS boots into RAM
    S2->>HTTP: GET system-2-final.ign
    HTTP->>S2: Flattened Ignition JSON

    Note over S2: coreos-installer writes to /dev/sda
    Note over S2: Reboot into installed FCOS
    Note over S2: prep-machine.service runs

    S2->>REG: bootc switch (pull hypervisor image)
    REG->>S2: hypervisor_node:latest

    Note over S2: Final reboot into persistent hypervisor
